      ## Stack

      Apply stack space below block-level elements to normalize vertical distance between components.

      <img src="/images/stack@2x.png" alt="Stack at X (8px), 2X (16px), or 3X (24px)" />
 
      Use proximity to signal related elements. Use whitespace to form boundaries between components. 

      <img src="/images/stack-example@2x.png" alt="Stack example: a list showing stacking items and stacking of blocks within an item" />
  

